What is API Gateway?
Managed service for creating APIs.
Acts as front door for backend services.

Architecture:
Client
   ↓
API Gateway
   ↓
Lambda

Features:
Authentication
Authorization
Rate Limiting
Monitoring
Versioning

Real-Time Scenario:
Food Delivery App

Mobile App
     ↓
API Gateway
     ↓
Lambda
     ↓
DynamoDB

User requests order details through APIs.

Benefits:
Secure APIs
Scalable APIs
Monitoring Built-In
